imdb.plot outline: Ricardo is a young, athletic, and a single father. He has a daughter, Alicia of 8 years old who is the world to him. Ricardo returns to his country due to a job offer without knowing that behind this business opportunity is Matilde, Catalina's grandmother. Upon his return, Ricardo meets Colomba, a young teacher who dreams of finding true love and believes she has found it in Ricardo. However, things won't be any easy for Colomba since Alicia doesn't like her and finds her unfit to be her father's girlfriend and to make matters worse, Catalina, Alicia's real mother; has return to Ricardo's life thanks to the little girl, who really likes her without knowing they are related. Ricardo will do anything to keep Alicia away from Catalina however Catalina will do everything in her power to make Colomba's life miserable and win her daughter back and above all, win over Ricardo's heart again.
imdb.title: Papi Ricky
plot: The relationship between Ricky and his daughter will suffer when the girl's mother returns and wants her back.::Anonymous

Ricardo is a young, athletic, and a single father. He has a daughter, Alicia of 8 years old who is the world to him. Ricardo returns to his country due to a job offer without knowing that behind this business opportunity is Matilde, Catalina's grandmother. Upon his return, Ricardo meets Colomba, a young teacher who dreams of finding true love and believes she has found it in Ricardo. However, things won't be any easy for Colomba since Alicia doesn't like her and finds her unfit to be her father's girlfriend and to make matters worse, Catalina, Alicia's real mother; has return to Ricardo's life thanks to the little girl, who really likes her without knowing they are related. Ricardo will do anything to keep Alicia away from Catalina however Catalina will do everything in her power to make Colomba's life miserable and win her daughter back and above all, win over Ricardo's heart again.::Latin Media Corp
